Product description

  • 8 Sports Modes with GPS Enabled

Turn on the GPS through the APP to meet your need to record the movement route

Your Intelligent Assistant

  • Heart Rate Monitor: 24h continuous heart rate monitoring
  • Blood Oxygen Monitor: Know your exercise intensity
  • Women's Health Tracking: track menstrual time and menstrual reminder
  • Breath Training: Improve lung function, prevent respiratory diseases
  • Music Control: Easily enjoy music switching during exercise
  • Alarm Clock: Remind you of your important agenda
  • Blood pressure: Monitor your blood pressure (not for medical data)

Features & details

Features

  • 【Your Excellent Daily Assistant】 With its 1.3-inch TFT-LCD full-touch screen. It offering crucial features like sleep monitoring, sports recording, menstrual health tracking, relaxation guidance, alarms, timers, and more, it's your health aide.
  • 【24/7 Heart Rate Monitoring & Sleep Tracking】 Keep track of your real-time heart rate throughout the day and effortlessly monitor your sleep patterns (Deep sleep, Light sleep, and Awake time). This feature offers valuable insights into the duration and quality of your sleep, assisting you in making lifestyle adjustments for an improved state of well-being.
  • 【Long-lasting Battery Life & 50 Meters Waterproof】Smart Watches feature a 50 Meters waterproof rating, meet your daily needs and swimming needs. The smart integration of a large-capacity battery and low power consumption ensures extended endurance. Offering up to 7 days of regular use and an impressive standby time of 35 days, this smartwatch provides both reliability and convenience.
  • 【Multiple movement modes】 This fitness tracker boasts Multiple sports modes. It accurately tracks and records your entire day's activities, keeping tabs on steps taken, calories burned, distance covered, active minutes, and more, meet your daily needs
  • 【Compatible with Android & iOS】This smartwatch is compatible with iOS 8.0+ and Android 4.4+ (Designed for use with smartphones only; not intended for PC, iPad, or Tablet use). Easily link up by downloading "VeryFitPro" app, pairing it with your cellphone, and receive timely alerts for calendar events, SMS, calls, and SNS notifications (Facebook, Twitter, Whatsapp, Skype, Snapchat, etc.).
